NOTICE OF INTENTION TO INTRODUCE LOCAL LEGISLATION
Notice is given that there will be introduced at the 2025 regular session
of the General Assembly of Georgia a bill to amend an Act creating a new
charter for the City of Conyers, approved March 16, 1978 (Ga. L. 1978, p.
3868), as amended; and for other purposes.
